So the CTFT of a periodic signal is a series of delta functions, each scaled by its corresponding CTFS coefficients (<link target-id="fig24"/>).</para>

<figure id="fig24" orient="vertical"><media id="CTFTCTFS" alt="">
       <image mime-type="" src="../../media/i1_1bdelta.png"/>
